Revision history for perl module SQL::Functional

0.3 2016-12-01

- Implement string literal clauses
- ::Clause->get_params() recurses into subclauses by default
- Add COUNT(...) clause

0.2 2016-10-17

- Remove v5.14 dependency
- Fix undeclared deps
- Autogenerate META.yml
- Add new clauses: LIMIT, TRUNCATE, DISTINCT
- Allow subqueries in FROM clause
- Add function calls
- Implement all standard join types

0.1 2016-07-30

- Initial release
